RUMORS ABOUT ME.

263
00:19:40,333 --> 00:19:43,083
- OH, YEAH?
AN OLD GIRLFRIEND MAYBE?

264
00:19:43,166 --> 00:19:45,333
- WELL, YOU SOUND
AWFULLY IRRITATED.

265
00:19:45,416 --> 00:19:47,916
- AND YOU'RE TREATING
RENTON PRETTY BADLY.

266
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,625
- IT'S NOT BAD TREATMENT.

267
00:19:49,708 --> 00:19:52,458
IT'S JUST HE IS...
HE'S DANGEROUS, THAT'S ALL.

268
00:19:52,541 --> 00:19:55,333
- AND WHICH FOOL DID THAT
DANGEROUS BOY SAVE?

269
00:19:55,416 --> 00:19:56,583
- HUH?

270
00:19:56,666 --> 00:19:59,375
- YOU WENT OFF AND TRIED
TO SAVE EUREKA.

271
00:19:59,458 --> 00:20:00,916
BUT, AT THE SAME TIME,

272
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:03,458
